1. Anil and Bhaskar can do a piece of work individually in 12 and 20 days respectively. They work together for 6 days before Anil decides to leave. How many days will it take Bhaskar to complete the work on his own?
A. 4 
B. 14 
C. 6
D. 3
Answer:option A
2. Dilip and Samrat can do a piece of work in 16 days and 24 days respectively. Samrat works alone for 15 days and leaves. In how many days can Dilip complete the remaining work?
A. 8 
B. 10
C. 6 
D. 7
Answer:option c
